abstract: "Research code, benchmark data, and experimental artifacts for PlanSafeBench-EVM, a semantic-policy validation benchmark and framework for pre-signing safety checks of AI-generated EVM transaction plans. Release v1.3.1 includes the corrected v5.6 benchmark, LLM audit results, harmonized counterfactual robustness results, and expert validation v0.4 summary artifacts."

